8.0, 1513.0]]], "lines": ["ククク", "よく分かったな"]}], "img_path": "0144.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1350, "img_height": 1920, "blocks": [{"box": [993, 211, 1147, 580], "vertical": true, "font_size": 37, "lines_coords": [[[1108.0, 211.0], [1145.0, 211.0], [1147.0, 541.0], [1110.0, 541.0]]], "lines": ["ねぇさっきの通行止め"]}, {"box": [992, 369, 1064, 586], "vertical": true, "font_size": 29, "lines_coords": [[[1031.0, 369.0], [1063.0, 369.0], [1063.0, 586.0], [1031.0, 586.0]], [[995.0, 369.0], [1021.0, 369.0], [1021.0, 555.0], [995.0, 555.0]]], "lines": ["何で通れるって", "知ってたの？"]}, {"box": [645, 135, 688, 208], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32, "lines_coords": [[[645.0, 135.0], [688.0, 135.0], [688.0, 208.0], [645.0, 208.0]]], "lines": ["あぁ"]}, {"box": [549, 165, 611, 504], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32, "lines_coords": [[[585.0, 165.0], [611.0, 165.0], [611.0, 504.0], [585.0, 504.0]], [[549.0, 166.0], [575.0, 166.0], [575.0, 474.0], [549.0, 474.0]]], "lines": ["前に家族と車で出掛けた時", "似たような事があってさ"]}, {"box": [689, 667, 753, 1059], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26, "lines_coords": [[[723.0, 667.0], [750.0, 667.0], [750.0, 920.0], [723.0, 920.0]], [[690.0, 667.0], [714.0, 667.0], [714.0, 1059.0], [690.0, 1059.0]]], "lines": ["引き返そうとしたら、", "地元の人が教えてくれたんだよ"]}, {"box": [136, 661, 201, 1096], "vertical": true, "font_size": 30, "lines_coords": [[[168.0, 661.0], [200.0, 661.0], [200.0, 928.0], [168.0, 928.0]], [[136.0, 663.0], [163.0, 663.0], [163.0, 1096.0], [136.0, 1096.0]]], "lines": ["「工事の人がカンバン", "置き忘れてるけど道は通れる」って"]}, {"box": [990, 1222, 1147, 1284], "vertical": false, "font_size": 39, "lines_coords": [[[995.0, 1222.0], [1147.0, 1245.0], [1141.0, 1284.0], [990.0, 1261.0]]], "lines": ["『止めなう』"]}, {"box": [744, 1145, 810, 1460], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26, "lines_coords": [[[781.0, 1149.0], [808.0, 1149.0], [808.0, 1428.0], [781.0, 1428.0]], [[744.0, 1145.0], [770.0, 1145.0], [772.0, 1460.0], [746.0, 1460.0]]], "lines": ["柵も端に寄ってたから", "もしかしてと思ってなー"]}, {"box": [594, 1176, 663,