1.0, 810.0], [1171.0, 933.0], [1130.0, 933.0]]], "lines": ["大垣．．．"]}, {"box": [80, 373, 151, 683], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32, "lines_coords": [[[118.0, 373.0], [150.0, 373.0], [151.0, 682.0], [120.0, 682.0]], [[80.0, 373.0], [112.0, 373.0], [112.0, 590.0], [80.0, 590.0]]], "lines": ["たまにはグルキャンも", "楽しいと思うぞ"]}, {"box": [185, 806, 219, 992], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32, "lines_coords": [[[185.0, 808.0], [217.0, 808.0], [217.0, 991.0], [185.0, 991.0]]], "lines": ["しまりん．．．"]}, {"box": [1081, 1385, 1171, 1576], "vertical": true, "font_size": 42, "lines_coords": [[[1125.0, 1385.0], [1171.0, 1385.0], [1171.0, 1505.0], [1125.0, 1505.0]], [[1081.0, 1387.0], [1119.0, 1387.0], [1119.0, 1576.0], [1081.0, 1576.0]]], "lines": ["それは", "遠慮しとく"]}], "img_path": "0146.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1350, "img_height": 1920, "blocks": [{"box": [1171, 157, 1203, 376], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32, "lines_coords": [[[1171.0, 157.0], [1203.0, 157.0], [1203.0, 376.0], [1171.0, 376.0]]], "lines": ["やっぱフラれた"]}, {"box": [765, 136, 840, 416], "vertical": true, "font_size": 33, "lines_coords": [[[802.0, 136.0], [840.0, 136.0], [838.0, 416.0], [800.0, 416.0]], [[765.0, 138.0], [793.0, 138.0], [796.0, 292.0], [768.0, 292.0]]], "lines": ["ガンコなソロキャン", "ガールだぜ"]}, {"box": [592, 245, 657, 661], "vertical": true, "font_size": 25, "lines_coords": [[[628.0, 247.0], [652.0, 247.0], [652.0, 658.0], [628.0, 658.0]], [[592.0, 247.0], [618.0, 247.0], [618.0, 513.0], [592.0, 513.0]]], "lines": ["みんなでキャンフできたらって", "思ってたんだけど．．．"]}, {"box": [151, 116, 184, 309], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27, "lines_coords": [[[151.0, 116.0], [178.0, 116.0], [178.0, 305.0], [151.0, 305.0]]], "lines": ["ちょっと残念。"]}, {"box": [735, 596, 766, 733], "vertical": true, "font_size": 31, "lines_coords": [[[735.0, 596.0], [766.0, 596.0], [766.0, 733.0], [735.0, 733.0]]], "lines": ["そっかぁ"]}, {"box": [292, 895, 642, 936], "vertical": false, "font_size": 27, "lines_coords": [[[305.0, 901.0], [628.0, 901.0], [628.0, 928.0], [305.0, 928.0]]], "lines": ["お早うでさいまーす"]}, {"box": [1102, 1284, 1179, 1387], "vertical": true, "font_size": 41, "lines_coords": [[[1138.0, 1286.0], [1179.0, 1286.0], [1179.0, 1385.0], [1138.0, 1385.0]], [[1102.0, 1284.0], [1143.0, 1284.0], [1143.0, 1387.0], [1102.0, 1387.0]]], "lines": ["ブーン", "ブーン"]}, {"box": [847, 1293, 884, 1522], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32, "lines_coords": [[[849.0, 1293.0], [881.0, 1293.0], [879.0, 1522.0], [847.0, 1522.0]]], "lines": ["む、今度は斉藤か"]}, {"box": [271, 1089, 660, 1198], "vertical": false, "font_size": 27, "lines_coords": [[[279.0, 1093.0], [570.0, 1093.0], [570.0, 1119.0], [279.0, 1119.0]], [[279.0, 1130.0], [626.0, 1130.0], [626.0, 1156.0], [279.0, 1156.0]], [[275.0, 1164.0], [660.0, 1168.0], [660.0, 1198.0], [275.0, 1194.0]]], "lines": ["３時頃起きたんだけど", "布団の包容力に寝落ちして", "しまいましたー＊＊｀＿＿＿＊"]}, {"box": [194, 1254, 569, 1295], "vertical": false, "font_size": 27, "lines_coords": [[[208.0, 1261.0], [555.0, 1261.0], [555.0, 1288.0], [208.0, 1288.0]]], "lines": ["４時間も寝てたのかよ"]}], "img_path": "0147.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1350, "img_height": 1920, "blocks": [{"box": [777, 160, 1183, 252], "vertical": false, "font_size": 27, "lines_coords": [[[785.0, 163.0], [1155.0, 163.0], [1155.0, 189.0], [785.0, 189.0]], [[783.0, 191.0], [1183.0, 191.0], [1183.0, 223.0], [783.0, 223.0]], [[785.0, 225.0], [1029.0, 225.0], [1029.0, 249.0], [785.0, 249.0]]], "lines": ["そういえば今度野クルの子たちと", "キャンプ行く事にしたよ（＊｀ェ｀＊）", "クリスマスキャンプー"]}, {"box": [735, 315, 1052, 382], "vertical": false, "font_size": 33, "lines_coords": [[[735.0, 316.0], [1050.0, 315.0], [1050.0, 346.0], [735.0, 348.0]], [[738.0, 348.0], [873.0, 348.0], [873.0, 382.0], [738.0, 382.0]]], "lines": ["あ、それ大垣から誘われた", "断ったけど"]}, {"box": [189, 326, 555, 426], "vertical": false, "font_size": 34, "lines_coords": [[[189.0, 326.0], [549.0, 326.0], [549.0, 365.0], [189.0, 365.0]], [[189.0, 356.0], [515.0, 356.0], [515.0, 393.0], [189.0, 393.0]], [[193.0, 395.0], [530.0, 395.0], [530.0, 421.0], [193.0, 421.0]]], "lines": ["えー！なでしこちゃんリンと", "クリスマスキャンプするの", "楽しみだって言うってたのに！"]}, {"box": [316, 594, 475, 633], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32, "lines_coords": [[[316.0, 596.0], [465.0, 596.0], [465.0, 628.0], [316.0, 628.0]]], "lines": ["ウソかい"]}, {"box": [201, 491, 377, 530], "vertical": false, "font_size": 27, "lines_coords": [[[204.0, 496.0], [365.0, 496.0], [365.0, 523.0], [204.0, 523.0]]], "lines": ["ウソだけど"]}, {"box": [161, 742, 634, 810], "vertical": false, "font_size": 35, "lines_coords": [[[163.0, 744.0], [581.0, 744.0], [581.0, 776.0], [163.0, 776.0]], [[161.0, 772.0], [633.0, 772.0], [633.0, 810.0], [161.0, 810.0]]], "lines": ["でも、一回だけ一緒に行ってみない？", "リンは一人キャンプの方が好きかもだけど"]}, {"box": [160, 862, 642, 928], "vertical": false, "font_size": 30, "lines_coords": [[[166.0, 866.0], [459.0, 864.0], [459.0, 896.0], [166.0, 898.0]], [[168.0, 901.0], [637.0, 901.0], [637.0, 928.0], [168.0, 928.0]]], "lines": ["みんなでやるキャンプは", "違うジャンルの楽しさがあると思うよ？"]}, {"box": [1153, 1140, 1196, 1237], "vertical": true, "font_size": 43, "lines_coords": [[[1153.0, 1140.0], [1196.0, 1140.0], [1196.0, 1237.0], [1153.0, 1237.0]]], "lines": ["ペコン"]}, {"box": [310, 1753, 744, 1827], "vertical": false, "font_size": 35, "lines_coords": [[[315.0, 1756.0], [740.0, 1756.0], [740.0, 1788.0], [315.0, 1788.0]], [[311.0, 1788.0], [729.0, 1788.0], [729.0, 1826.0], [311.0, 1826.0]]], "lines": ["リンちゃん！！ボクといっしょに", "クリスマスキャンプいこうよ！！"]}], "img_path": "0148.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1350, "img_height": 1920, "blocks": [{"box": [274, 169, 621, 205], "vertical": false, "font_size": 26, "lines_coords": [[[288.0, 176.0], [616.0, 176.0], [616.0, 202.0], [288.0, 202.0]]], "lines": ["じゃ私こっころ寝るよー"]}, {"box": [210, 265, 535, 333], "vertical": false, "font_size": 36, "lines_coords": [[[211.0, 266.0], [397.0, 266.0], [397.0, 298.0], [211.0, 298.0]], [[210.0, 294.0], [528.0, 294.0], [528.0, 333.0], [210.0, 333.0]]], "lines": ["まだ寝るのかよ", "もう布団と結婚してしまえ"]}, {"box": [256, 390, 629, 484], "vertical": false, "f